@@$TJvAppAnimatedIcon
<GROUP JVCL.Miscel>
<TITLE TJvAppAnimatedIcon overview>
  The TJvAppAnimatedIcon component allows you to make an animated application icon. The component
  will change the applications icon every interval by cycling a list of icons.

  To create an application with an animated icon you should execute the following tasks:

  * Drop a TJvAppAnimatedIcon component on a form or data module.
  * Set the <LINK TJvAppAnimatedIcon.Delay, animation interval> to an appropiate value.
  * <LINK TJvAppAnimatedIcon,Icons, Link the component to an image list> containing the icons to
    use for animation.
  * <LINK TJvAppAnimatedIcon.Active, Activate> the component.
