@@TJvAppAnimatedIcon
<GROUP TJvAppAnimatedIcon>
Summary
  Animates the application's icon.
Description
  This component allows you to make an animated application icon. The component will change the
  applications icon every interval by cycling a list of icons.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAppAnimatedIcon.Animate
Summary
  Selects the next icon.
Description
  Animate is called every interval to select a new icon for the application.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAppAnimatedIcon.SetActive
Summary
  Changes the active state.
Description
  SetActive changes the active state of the component. It's the write method for the Active
  property.
See Also
  Active
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAppAnimatedIcon.SetDelay
Summary
  Changes the animation interval.
Description
  SetDelay changes the animation interval. It's the write method for the Delay property.
See Also
  Delay
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAppAnimatedIcon.SetImgList
Summary
  Changes the icon list to use.
Description
  SetImgList changes the list of icons. It's the write method for the Icons property.
See Also
  Icons
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAppAnimatedIcon.Active
Summary
  Indicates wether the application icon is animated.
Description
  Active indicates wether or not the component is active and the application icon is animated. When
  set to True, the application icon will change at the specified interval, otherwise the application
  icon will not change.
See Also
  Delay, Icons
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAppAnimatedIcon.Delay
Summary
  The interval between two icon changes.
Description
  Delay is the delay in milliseconds before the application icon changes.
See Also
  Active, Icons
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAppAnimatedIcon.Icons
Summary
  The list of icons used for animation.
Description
  Icons is an image list, containing the icons to use in the animation.
